The paper discusses the development of a column-oriented datastore for PowerDrill, which is a system for answering ad hoc queries over large datasets in an interactive manner. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the database (cs.DB), data structures (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), software engineering (cs.SE), or human-computer interaction (cs.HCI) sub-categories.
